Description: Indulge yourself in the luxurious fragrance of ‘Coco Mademoiselle’ from the house of Chanel. It is a Chypre floral fragrance for women. ‘Coco Mademoiselle’ was first introduced in 2001 and was created by Jacques Polge. This chic perfume has a sophisticated fragrance with a woody hint. It has a high note of floral scents like mandarin orange, bergamot, orange blossom; the middle notes are jasmine, mimose, ylang-ylang and Turkish rose; with the lower notes being opoponax, tonka bean, vanilla, patchouli, white musk and vetiver . However, the best part of ‘Coco Mademoiselle’ is that with all the notes it still does not smell of any particular flower. You can catch passing hints of each every now and then. It has a fresh, and oriental fragrance that lingers for a long time. Each spray of the ‘Coco Mademoiselle’ reflects the spirit of the brand that ‘Chanel’. The scent is rich and gently caresses the pulse points and gives off a fruity and floral scent in the beginning which changes its tone on dry-down. ‘Coco Mademoiselle’ is suitable for both formal occasions as well as casual night outs and is especially suitable during the winter seasons.The Coco Mademoiselle EDP comes in a classy square bottle with a matte white cap which emulates a classic charm and is a perfect addition to your dresser. So buy Chanel’s Coco Mademoiselle EDP and enjoy the grand feel of it.

It can improve inflammatory pustular, comedonal, and papular acne and has been shown to be effective even in individuals resistant to antibiotics.
